# Project Goals: ProtoFusionGirl (2025-06-04)

## Vision
- Create a next-generation, AI-optimized, artifact-driven game with deep lore and emergent systems
- Make Universal Magic and Universal Language core to all gameplay, narrative, and world systems
- Enable player agency to shape timelines, realities, and outcomes through skillful use of magic and technology

## Key Goals
- Seamless integration of reality warping, anchor systems, and Timestream Framework
- Replayability through procedural content, timeline branching, and anchor sharing
- Accessibility, modding, and community-driven content as first-class features
